IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. BillingEngine.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-PREMIUM       PIC 9(9)V99.
01 WS-MONTHS        PIC 9(2).
01 WS-MONTHLY       PIC 9(9)V99.
01 WS-ANNUAL        PIC 9(9)V99.
01 WS-TAX-RATE      PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 0.10.
01 WS-TAX           PIC 9(9)V99.
01 WS-TOTAL         PIC 9(9)V99.

LINKAGE SECTION.
01 LK-PREMIUM       PIC 9(9)V99.
01 LK-MONTHS        PIC 9(2).
01 LK-TOTAL         PIC 9(9)V99.
01 LK-RESULT        PIC X(200).

PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LK-PREMIUM LK-MONTHS
                         LK-TOTAL LK-RESULT.

    MOVE LK-PREMIUM TO WS-PREMIUM.
    MOVE LK-MONTHS  TO WS-MONTHS.

    IF WS-MONTHS = 0
        MOVE 12 TO WS-MONTHS
    END-IF.

    COMPUTE WS-MONTHLY = WS-PREMIUM / 12.
    COMPUTE WS-ANNUAL  = WS-MONTHLY * WS-MONTHS.
    COMPUTE WS-TAX     = WS-ANNUAL  * WS-TAX-RATE.
    COMPUTE WS-TOTAL   = WS-ANNUAL  + WS-TAX.

    MOVE WS-TOTAL TO LK-TOTAL.

    STRING 'MONTHLY=' WS-MONTHLY
           ' MONTHS=' WS-MONTHS
           ' TAX='    WS-TAX
           ' TOTAL='  WS-TOTAL
           DELIMITED SIZE INTO LK-RESULT.

    GOBACK.